Package com.paulscode.sound.codecs

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CodecIBXM
    The CodecIBXM class provides an ICodec interface for reading from MOD/S3M/XM files via the IBXM library.
    CodecJOgg
    The CodecJOgg class provides an ICodec interface to the external J-Ogg library.
    CodecJOrbis
    The CodecJOrbis class provides an ICodec interface to the external JOrbis library.
    CodecJSpeex
    The CodecJSpeex class provides an ICodec interface for reading from files encoded by Speex.
    CodecWav
    The CodecWav class provides an ICodec interface for reading from .wav files.
